Package: libfusepromise1
Section: libs
Architecture: any
Multi-Arch: same
Depends:
 ${shlibs:Depends},
 ${misc:Depends}
Description: Promise filesystem public C ABI runtime library
 libfusepromise provides the stable public C ABI used by applications and
 providers that integrate with the fuse-promise user-session filesystem
 runtime.

Package: libfusepromise-dev
Section: libdevel
Architecture: any
Multi-Arch: same
Depends:
 libfusepromise1 (= ${binary:Version}),
 pkgconf | pkg-config,
 ${misc:Depends}
Description: Development files for libfusepromise
 This package contains the public C header, unversioned shared library symlink,
 and pkg-config metadata needed to build applications against libfusepromise.

Package: fuse3-promise
Architecture: any
Depends:
 ${shlibs:Depends},
 ${misc:Depends},
 libfusepromise1 (= ${binary:Version}),
 fuse3
Provides:
 fuse-promise
Conflicts:
 fuse-promise
Replaces:
 fuse-promise
Description: Promise filesystem runtime built on FUSE 3
 fuse-promise provides a user-session FUSE daemon and an administrative CLI for
 mounting Promise filesystem providers through FUSE 3. The public C ABI is
 shipped by the libfusepromise runtime and development packages.
